OL,6,FA 76-year-old man who spent five days
OL,7,Fin A&E at Altnagelvin Hospital in
OL,8,FLondonderry, says that sheer
OL,9,Fexhaustion caused him to hallucinate.
OL,11,FKen Thatcher who suffers from Crohn's
OL,12,Fdisease (an inflammatory bowel
OL,13,Fcondition), said inadequate facilities
OL,14,Fin the Emergency Department made his
OL,15,Flong wait for a bed even more
OL,16,Funpleasant.
