OL,3,CCo. Derry man spent five days waiting
OL,4,Cfor a bed in Altnagelvin A&E
OL,6,FMr. Thatcher, owner of a literary
OL,7,Flandmark shop in Derry and a man of
OL,8,Fwords, wrote an online blog detailing
OL,9,Fa story not found on his shelves: his
OL,10,F120-hour wait in A&E.
OL,12,FHe said he was taken to the emergency
OL,13,Fdepartment due to a flare-up.
OL,15,FDuring his five-day stay, spent mostly
OL,16,Fon a chair or trolley, he faced
OL,17,Fadditional indignity due to a lack of
OL,18,Ftoilet facilities and even began to
OL,19,Fhallucinate.
