OL,3,CCo. Derry man spent five days waiting
OL,4,Cfor a bed in Altnagelvin A&E
OL,6,FAltnagelvin's ED is the oldest in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland and is severely
OL,8,Fovercrowded.
OL,10,FIt was built for around 40,000 annual
OL,11,Fpatient visits but now sees 70,000
OL,12,Fpatients, leading to long waits and
OL,13,Fcramped conditions.
OL,15,FToday, people at Alnagelvin face
OL,16,Flonger waits than at any other
OL,17,Fhospital.
OL,19,FWhile plans for redevelopment are
OL,20,Fbeing drawn up, they are currently
OL,21,Funaffordable.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
