OL,3,CCo. Derry man spent five days waiting
OL,4,Cfor a bed in Altnagelvin A&E
OL,6,FThe Health Minister, who witnessed the
OL,7,Fdifficult conditions firsthand said:
OL,8,F"It was pretty shocking particulary
OL,9,Fthe toileting facilities."
OL,11,FHe continued: " A traunch of money has
OL,12,Fbeen has found to do some temporary
OL,13,Fwork in the existing ED pending the
OL,14,Fbuilding of the new ED, that's years
OL,15,Fnot months away."
OL,17,FThe Western Trust stated patients are
OL,18,Freceiving the best possible care
OL,19,Fduring this challenging time.
